Package od.oracle.apps.xxom.atp

Class Summary
ATPConstants Provides all the necessary Constants for the ATP application.
ATPMakeCall Implements the execution of database PL/SQL procedure.
ATPProcessControl This is the standard API to be used to call the Custom ATP with the required parameters.
ATPRecordType Object type of the ATP inquiry.
ATPResultSetType Proides an object type to load all the results of an ATP inquiry.
DateAnalysis This class analyses all the results to find the best date available for the particular item inquiry.
InputValidation Validation class performs necessary validation of the data.
LogATP Class to log the data manipulated in this application.Temporary use as for debugging.
PreProcess This Class executes the PreProcess step of the ATP process.
